=version 1
=resource Channel
=method get
=endpoint /channels/:id/follow
=description Lists users who follow a channel.

include ../../_mixins.jade

p This endpoint lists users who follow a channel, in the order that they followed.

h3 Parameters

table.endpoint-param-table
    tr
        td.name :id
        td.description Numeric ID of the channel to look up.
    tr
        td.name page #[span optional]
        td.description
            | Page of results to get.
            .default 0
    tr
        td.name limit #[span optional]
        td.description
            | Number of results per page to retrieve.
            .default 50

